lead_paragraph: Rookie Emmanuel Mudiay scored nine of his 15 points during a decisive fourth-quarter run, and the Denver Nuggets beat the fading New York Knicks 101-96 on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Mudiay, Nuggets Hand Knicks 5th Straight Loss
